PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of V. MAUREEN KEMPSTON DARKES, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective March 29, 1995, in the place of H. Donald Guthrie, who has resigned.
